GOAL

Transform Med-Peptides into a white-label, territory-based franchise platform for wholesalers and regional partners.

The platform must allow wholesalers to operate Med-Peptides as if it were their own platform in assigned territories and product categories, while Med-Peptides remains the central technology and catalog infrastructure.

Do NOT redesign the entire app.
Extend the current architecture.

Keep:
- Firebase
- Google Cloud Agent Platform
- ClinicAI
- Product catalog
- Protocol engine
- Territory protection engine
- Geography Areas page

────────────────────────
BUSINESS OBJECTIVE
────────────────────────

Wholesalers must feel comfortable that:

1. Their clients remain assigned to them.
2. Their territory is protected.
3. Their brand can appear in the platform.
4. Their doctors and clinics are not exposed to Med-Peptides direct pricing.
5. Their customers are not reassigned to another partner.
6. Their URL/domain can feel independent.
7. Their categories and territories are configurable.

Med-Peptides acts as:
central platform provider.

Wholesaler acts as:
regional franchise / partner / commercial operator.

────────────────────────
CORE CONCEPT
────────────────────────

Create a multi-tenant white-label architecture.

Main entity:

tenant

A tenant can be:
- wholesaler
- regional partner
- clinic group
- distributor
- internal Med-Peptides market

────────────────────────
TENANT DATA MODEL
────────────────────────

Create Firebase collection:

tenants

Example:

{
  "tenantId": "magenta-uae",
  "name": "Magenta",
  "type": "wholesaler",
  "status": "active",

  "territories": ["AE"],

  "categories": [
    "peptide_vials",
    "compounded_formulations"
  ],

  "branding": {
    "logoUrl": "",
    "faviconUrl": "",
    "primaryColor": "",
    "secondaryColor": "",
    "accentColor": "",
    "supportEmail": "",
    "supportWhatsapp": "",
    "footerText": ""
  },

  "domain": {
    "mode": "subdomain",
    "url": "magenta.med-peptides.com",
    "customDomain": null
  },

  "commercialRules": {
    "hidePricesForGuests": true,
    "allowCheckout": false,
    "defaultCTA": "Contact your clinic"
  }
}

────────────────────────
URL STRATEGY
────────────────────────

Support three URL modes:

1. Subdomain:
magenta.med-peptides.com

2. Custom domain:
protocols.magenta.ae

3. Path-based fallback:
med-peptides.com/partners/magenta

Recommended implementation order:

Phase 1:
Path-based tenant routing.

Phase 2:
Subdomain tenant routing.

Phase 3:
Custom domain support.

────────────────────────
TENANT RESOLUTION
────────────────────────

Create:

resolveTenant()

Inputs:
- hostname
- URL path
- referral code
- logged user profile
- assigned wholesaler
- activeCommercialTerritory

Resolution priority:

1. custom domain
2. subdomain
3. path tenant slug
4. logged user tenantId
5. referral link
6. territory default tenant
7. Med-Peptides default

────────────────────────
CUSTOMER OWNERSHIP
────────────────────────

Every user, lead, cart and order must store:

tenantId
ownerType
ownerId
sourceDomain
sourceTerritory
attributionLocked

Example:

{
  "tenantId": "magenta-uae",
  "ownerType": "wholesaler",
  "ownerId": "magenta",
  "sourceDomain": "magenta.med-peptides.com",
  "attributionLocked": true
}

Once attributionLocked is true:
do not reassign customer automatically.

Only admin can override.

────────────────────────
CLIENT PROTECTION RULE
────────────────────────

Wholesalers must only see:

- their assigned clients
- their assigned doctors
- their assigned orders
- their assigned territories
- their assigned categories

Wholesalers must NOT see:

- other wholesalers’ clients
- Med-Peptides direct clients outside their territory
- other protected territories
- hidden admin margins

────────────────────────
WHITE-LABEL BRANDING
────────────────────────

Implement dynamic branding by tenant.

Tenant controls:

- logo
- colors
- favicon
- support contact
- WhatsApp contact
- footer
- CTA wording
- displayed business name
- prescription instructions
- clinic referral text

Create:

TenantBrandProvider

This wraps the application and injects branding.

If tenant missing:
use Med-Peptides default branding.

