────────────────────────
SUCCESS CRITERIA
────────────────────────

A wholesaler can operate a branded version of the platform.

Users from that version are assigned to the wholesaler.

Prices and checkout follow territory/category rules.

ClinicAI respects tenant rules.

No customer leakage.

No URL conflict.

No duplicated codebase.

Med-Peptides remains the central infrastructure.